name: Meta-carpal pain reborn
description:
Growing up through different lives yet
seeing and feeling a mutual vision
brought us together, to spread our
message, to feel our pain and to feel
our love. This thing we all call life has
many ups and downs and the downs
can consume you only when YOU let
them. Life is what you make of it and
the energy you feed into is what you
will receive the most, never feed the
negatives even when they are heavily
breathing down your neck. We are the
same, living in separate avatars.
Yusaymon x CullenColors
